issue.title: [CF 667] Missing CC's from debuff categories
issue.body:
I've noticed that Intimidating Roar (113056) that the druid receives from buffing a warrior with symbiosis is missing. Blinding Light (115750) from paladins is missing, some stun associated with Combustion (118271) is missing, the Disorienting Roar (99) from Druids is missing. I assume other CC gained from Symbiosis will also be missing.


> Posted by CurseForge user AmeroGer | Imported from CurseForge issue #667 | Raw

comments.body:
Thanks. Will look into these when I get a chance.

Could you investigate the rest of the Symbiosis spells and see what other ones are missing?


> Posted by CurseForge user Cybeloras
